#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an3.21:9.1"
msgid "“Na khvettha, sāriputta, sukaraṃ ekaṃsena byākātuṃ:"
msgstr "“In this matter, Sāriputta, it’s not easy to definitively declare that"

msgctxt "an3.21:9.2"
msgid "‘ayaṃ imesaṃ tiṇṇaṃ puggalānaṃ abhikkantataro ca paṇītataro cā’ti."
msgstr "one of these three people is finest."

#. VAR: svāssa → svāyaṃ (s1-3, km, pts1) | soyaṃ (mr)
#. VAR: svāssa → svāyaṃ (s1-3, km, pts1) | soyaṃ (mr)
#. VAR: sopassa → soyaṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an3.21:9.3"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānañhetaṃ, sāriputta, vijjati yvāyaṃ puggalo saddhāvimutto svāssa "
"arahattāya paṭipanno, yvāyaṃ puggalo kāyasakkhī svāssa sakadāgāmī vā anāgāmī "
"vā, yo cāyaṃ puggalo diṭṭhippatto sopassa sakadāgāmī vā anāgāmī vā."
msgstr ""
"In some cases, a person who is freed by faith is practicing for perfection, "
"while the direct witness and the one attained to view are once-returners or "
"non-returners."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an3.21:10.1"
msgid "Na khvettha, sāriputta, sukaraṃ ekaṃsena byākātuṃ:"
msgstr "In this matter, it’s not easy to definitively declare that"

msgctxt "an3.21:10.2"
msgid "‘ayaṃ imesaṃ tiṇṇaṃ puggalānaṃ abhikkantataro ca paṇītataro cā’ti."
