msgctxt "an3.21:10.3"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānañhetaṃ, sāriputta, vijjati yvāyaṃ puggalo kāyasakkhī svāssa arahattāya "
"paṭipanno, yvāyaṃ puggalo saddhāvimutto svāssa sakadāgāmī vā anāgāmī vā, yo "
"cāyaṃ puggalo diṭṭhippatto sopassa sakadāgāmī vā anāgāmī vā."
msgstr ""
"In some cases, a direct witness is practicing for perfection, while the one "
"freed by faith and the one attained to view are once-returners or non-"
"returners."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
